section.div: ☁️ Help me cover my server and domains costs

div.p: A hobbyist developer working on creative open-source projects.

ul.li: 📊 metrics, a svg infographics generator for your GitHub profile
🍵 matcha, a drop-in pure css library for fast styling and prototyping
🌊 mizu, a minimalist html-templating library for all-side-rendering
🍱 libs, a collection of carefully crafted runtime-agnostic typescript libraries
🌺 gracidea, a Pokémon 2D live map with animated characters

div.p: I also contribute to 🦕 deno standard library sometimes, I'm the author of deepMerge, assertObjectMatch, string diff in Deno.test, and other minor patchs.
You can also check my other works on simon.lecoq.io 🦑
